:["Walking"],"geography":["Urban"],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Mode shift and demand management","purpose":"Promote active mobility","instrument":"Cycling measures","asi":["Shift"],"quote":"Les actions structurantes consisteront notamment en la création de parkingsrelais auxfrontières et à la multiplicité des solutions alternatives de mobilité (télécabines, soutien à la marcheà pied et à la pratique du vélo par le renforcement des équipementset des offres de e-services).","page":27,"modes":["Cycling"],"geography":["Urban"],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Electrification","purpose":"Promote electric mobility","instrument":"General e-mobility measures","asi":["Improve"],"quote":"En complément, le Gouvernement soutient la substitution des véhicules thermiques par des véhicules électriques. Si elle améliore la situation en termes d’émissions directes de CO2et de polluants atmosphériques, cette substitutionne résout pas les problèmes de congestion des axes de déplacement (qui conditionnent en premier lieu les possibilités de développement des modes alternatifs) et est difficilement généralisable (consommation et puissance électrique trèsimportante, risque d’incendie en parkings collectifs...).","page":27,"modes":["Road"],"geography":["Urban"],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Aviation and maritime","purpose":"Promote improvements in aviation","instrument":"Airport CO2 certification","asi":["Improve"],"quote":"Dans le cadre du transport aérien des efforts sont engagés pour limiter la consommation de carburant des aéronefs. L’héliport de Monaco poursuit une démarche de certification Airport Carbon Accreditation.","page":27,"modes":["Aviation"],"geography":[],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Electrification","purpose":"Promote electric mobility","instrument":"General e-mobility measures","asi":["Improve"],"quote":"Des hélicoptères électriques pourraient être mis en service à horizon 2030 pour assurer les lignes régulières Monaco –Nice (France).","page":27,"modes":["Aviation"],"geography":[],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Aviation and maritime","purpose":"Promote improvements in shipping","instrument":"General shipping improvement","asi":["Improve"],"quote":"Enfin s’agissant de la navigation, la Principauté a interdit l’utilisation de fioul lourd dans ses eaux territoriales","page":27,"modes":["Water"],"geography":[],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Aviation and maritime","purpose":"Promote improvements in shipping","instrument":"Support on-shore power and electric charging facilities in ports","asi":["Improve"],"quote":"et déploie des dispositifs pour l’alimentation électrique des navires dans les ports.","page":27,"modes":["Water"],"geography":[],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":17665,"document":"Second Generation NDC","version":"NDC 2.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Archived","category":"Alternative fuels","purpose":"Promote alternative fuels","instrument":"Hydrogen support measures","asi":["Improve"],"quote":"Des réflexions sont menées pour le recours à l’hydrogène par les navires.Ces politiques seront soutenues par une décarbonation progressive des carburants en lien avec les politiques européennes en la matière","page":27,"modes":["Water"],"geography":[],"measure_status":null},{"doc_id":79673,"document":"Third Generation NDC","version":"NDC 3.0","doc_type":"NDC","status":"Activ